title: Federal Judge Permanently Bars MetaBirkins NFT Maker From Selling Birkin-Based Collectibles
description: The judge’s order comes several months after a jury found the NFT collection’s maker infringed on Hermes’ intellectual property.

title: Congress Restricts Staff Access to ChatGPT to Protect Privacy
description: U.S. House staffers are told they must subscribe to ChatGPT Plus if they want to use the generative AI tool in their work.
